	<h2>Winter Activities</h2>
    <p>From the end of November to the first week of April, little else is on locals’ minds than the snow! The mountain is open daily from 9 am – 4 pm providing thrills for all. For those of you who aren’t interested in strapping plastic to your feet and plummeting down a mountain, Telluride has plenty of fun winter activities that can take place on flat land. Below is a list of things you need to try in Telluride this winter.</p>
